# Mobile-first application

This project is **mobile-first**. When changing UI, gestures, or layout:

- **Test on mobile viewports** (narrow/tall) as well as desktop. Zoom, pan, and tap behavior must work on touch devices.
- **Avoid desktop-only logic** for core interactions (e.g. hex grid zoom/pan/clamp apply to all viewports unless explicitly documented).
- **Real estate matters** on small screens: minimize empty space, avoid large padding or letterboxing when possible, and ensure tap targets are usable.
